        <unitName xml:lang="en">metric ton*km</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Transport distance based on US BTS Commodity Flow Surveys 1993, 1997, 2002, 2007, US Dep. Of Transportation, Bureau of Transportation Statistics. Of the total road transport, 6% is assumed to be by delivery van for goods with a large share of retail sale, and 3% for goods that are mainly sold via wholesale.

Estimation for hydrogen reduced by 90%.</comment>
